title: The Cedar Grill
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Lebanese food restaurant. Will prepare vegan food on separate surfaces and in separate pans when requested. Choices for vegans includes hummus, baba ghannouj, stuffed grape leaves, chick pea and mixed bean salad served with pita bread, rice with lentils, green beans with tomato and spices, tabbouleh, falafel and potatoes in tomato sauce served with a tahini sauce.
